00:05:34.449 --> 00:05:45.009
just read. There it says, and the wicked will be no more. Not only will Jehovah undo the damage

00:05:45.009 --> 00:05:49.649
that men have done, but he will also remove the source of the problem.

00:05:50.610 --> 00:05:56.050
Greedy men who exploit and misuse this precious resource will be gone.

00:05:57.250 --> 00:06:04.129
Therefore, we have no reason to fear that humans will continue to run the earth until it reaches

00:06:04.129 --> 00:06:13.970
the point of no return. Jehovah knows what is going on. Please open your Bibles to Revelation chapter 11

00:06:14.050 --> 00:06:21.329
and we'll read verse 18. This scripture assures us that Jehovah cares about our planet because

00:06:21.329 --> 00:06:29.730
it is his planet and it confirms that he is going to hold men accountable for their actions.

00:06:30.529 --> 00:06:38.370
Revelation chapter 11 verse 18 says, but the nations became wrathful and your own wrath came

00:06:39.089 --> 00:06:44.850
and the appointed time came for the dead to be judged and to reward your slaves the prophets

00:06:44.850 --> 00:06:53.649
and the holy ones and those fearing your name the small and the great and to bring to ruin those

00:06:53.649 --> 00:07:03.329
running the earth. Jehovah is not going to let wicked men run his beautiful creation.

00:07:04.290 --> 00:07:09.810
Nothing can stop Jehovah from carrying out his purpose for the earth.

00:07:11.250 --> 00:07:17.329
Our examination of the forest has strengthened our faith that Jehovah will accomplish everything

00:07:17.329 --> 00:07:25.089
that he has in mind to do. The words of faithful Job reflect our conviction that that promise

00:07:25.089 --> 00:07:32.449
will come true. As recorded at Job chapter 42 verse 2, Job was moved to declare regarding Jehovah,

00:07:33.170 --> 00:07:39.810
now I know that you are able to do all things and that nothing you have in mind to do

00:07:40.610 --> 00:07:49.490
is impossible for you. What does Jehovah have in mind to do? One thing is to transform the earth

00:07:49.490 --> 00:07:57.250
into a paradise with rich abundant forest. Forests that will continue to help sustain our

00:07:57.250 --> 00:08:04.449
supply of fresh water to purify our air and to convert carbon dioxide into oxygen.

